        <description>Rule Code: EM-001xFxx
Case Initial Response Time Update By Email
Updates the &quot;Case Initial Response Time&quot; field whenever there is an email sent by certain user profiles.</description>
        <formula>( $User.ProfileId = &apos;00e30000000bvR3&apos; || $User.ProfileId = &apos;00e50000000hvYj&apos; || $User.ProfileId = &apos;00e50000001BfGZ&apos; ) &amp;&amp; ( $User.Id &lt;&gt; &apos;00530000000f63s&apos; ) &amp;&amp; ( ISBLANK( Parent.Case_Initial_Response_Time__c ) )</formula>
